* Ingestion Tool\nLandscape
** Managed (Low Code)
***_ Lakeflow Connect
***_ Turnkey connectors
***_ Auto schema evolution
** Semi-Managed
***_ Auto Loader
***_ COPY INTO
** Custom / Code-First
***_ Spark Structured Streaming
***_ JDBC/ODBC notebooks
** Orchestration
***_ Azure Data Factory
***_ Broader Azure ecosystem
** Selection Factors
***_ Source type
***_ Latency requirements
***_ Maintenance overhead
***_ Team skills
